data.text:
5 Greatest Fandom [Anime/Manga] that You Treasure Deeply…

1. Minekura Fandom [I like all of her works, Saiyuki, Stigma, Bus Gamer, & Wild Adapter]

2. Air Gear

3. Katekyo Hitman Reborn

4. Beyblade <= no kidding, seriously, Kai Hiwatari is my Prince of angst :p

5. Yugi Oh! <= OMG!!! Yugi beats ES21 & Oofuri!!

5 Greatest Fandom [Game] that You Treasure Deeply

1. Gust Fandom [Atelier Series including Mana Khemia, Ar Tonelico series]

2. Pokemon

3. Xenosaga

4. Kingdom Hearts

5. Gyakuten Saiban Series <=yes, Gyakusai beats .hack series & Persona3

5 Greatest Artist that Your Adore So Much and is Your Greatest Inspiration…

1. Minekura Kazuya

2. Oh Great! [Oogure Ito] – Air Gear

3. Amano Akira – KHR

4. NAGI – Ar Tonelico

5. Matsumoto Temari – Kyou Kara Ma Ou!

5 Manga Title that You Want to Read Right Now…

1. Minekura Fandomcoughcough <=impossible to list them one by one cause I want to read all

2. Katekyo Hitman Reborn

3. Eyeshield21

4. Air Gear

5. Ookiku Furikabutte

5 Game Title that You Want to Play Right Now…

1. Gyakuten Kenji!!!!

2. Ar Tonelico 2

3. Final Fantasy Versus XIII <= where are you PS3?

4. Persona 4

5. Gyakuten Saiban 5 <= is this even announced? :p

5 Items You Want to Have Right Now…

1. Pen tablet for the sake of our beloved lineart >_<

2. Salty Dog 1 & 3 by Minekura Kazuya

3. Translated scans of Wild Adapter Vol 5 – 6

4. D18 doujinshis >_<

5. World’s greates free antivirus [I also want new hardisk T_T]

5 Doujinka that You Adore The Most…

1. Banyu [Aoi Levin] <= for wonderful D18

2. Nalis [Noriko Nanami] <= for wonderful 8059

3. Negahyst <= for wonderful ShinSena doujins

4. Jigen&Goemon(?) <= for wonderful AbeMiha doujins

5. Yukino Suzui(?) <= for wonderful NaruMitsu doujins

5 Fandom’s Pairing that You will Ship and will Never stop Shipping it…

1. D18 & 8059 – KHR

2. AgitoAkito – Air Gear

3. KuboToki, SanzoGoku, GojyoHakkai – Minekura Fandom

4. HirumaMamori, ShinSena – Eyeshield21 <= HET!!! HET!!! HET!!!!,the last one is shounen-ai

5. AbeMihashi – Oofuri

[actually, there’s TONS of them, but this is only 5]

5 Pairing that You’ll Ship even if You are The Only One Shipping Them…

1. MayBrendan/YuukiHaruka/RubyShapire – Pokemon <= they just meant to be >_<

2. AgitoAkito – Air Gear <= IkkiAki/IkkiAgi to hell

3. ZukoMai – Avatar <= who cares about Katara? She should go and accept our little Aang…

4. AkihikoMinato – Persona 3 <= ok, I’m seriously the only one or not?

5. AxelMarluxia – feel free to bulge your eyes out, feel free…

5 Pairing that You’ll never Ship even if Everyone Shipping Them…

1. ZukoKatara – Avatar <= the hell with Katara, Aang is waiting, hello?

2. Any pairing that get on the way of D18/8059 <= KHR

3. Any pairing that get on the way of HiruMamo/ShinSena <= Eyeshield21

4. ConradYuuri – KKM <= father and son, just that

5. AkihikoMitsuru – Persona 3 <= I’d rather die than seeing Akihiko touched by woman…

5 Pairing that You Find as ‘SHOTA’/’LOLI’…

1. AkihikoKen – Persona 3 <= MWAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAAHAHAHAHAHAHAHA!!!

2. GammaUni – KHR <= so adorable, so cute, so…

3. GurenMasahiro – Shounen Onmyouji <= can’t resist, I can’t…

4. D18 – KHR <= I hope 7 years differences counts…

5. TobariMiharu – Nabari no Ou <= ….. *run*

5 Pairing that Bear ‘-cest’ in Your Heart…

1. HikaruKaoru – Ouran Koukou Host Club <= Twincest Hitachi’ncest

2. AgitoAkito – Air Gear <= Technically Selfcest

3. HieiYukina – Yu Yu Hakusho <= Incest

4. FredGeorge – Harry Potter <= Twincest

5. LucaCroche – Ar Tonelico 2 <= Incest *run*

5 Character That You Want To Meet In Real World…

1. Dino Cavallone – KHR <= *looking for Itallian with appearance like Dino*

2. Klavier Gavin – Gyakuten Saiban

3. Miles Edgeworth – Gyakuten Saiban

4. Akihiko Sanada – Persona 3

5. L Lawliet – Death Note

5 Character that You Want to Kick their Ass for Touching Your Bishies/Girls…

1. Katara – Avatar <= it’s not that I hate you, please stay away from Zuko

2. Misa Amane – Death Note <= Stay away from Light, can’t you see he is all for L?*run*

3. Lyner Barsett – Ar Tonelico <= playboy like you deserve hell, thank you

4. Philomel Hartung – Mana Khemia <= Vayne is Gunnar’s, Anna’s, & Roxis’. Go, shoo~

5. Drew – Pokemon <= touch May again and you die.Seriously, I want Brendan!!!

5 Character that You Want to Hug for Their Awesomeness…

1. Dino Cavallone – KHR <= DINO-SAMA!!!!

2. AgitoAkito – Air Gear <= aww, so cute, so cute… *kicked by Agito*

3. Sanada Akihiko – Persona 3 <= senpai, I’ll put you away from girls!!!

4. Aurica Netsmile – Ar Tonelico <= I will put her away from that bastard named Lyner Barsett.

5. Mihasi Ren – Oofuri <= So cute, so adorable!!!! *huuuuuuuuugggg*

5 Het Pairings that You Love…

1. SetoKisara – Yugi Oh! <= no kidding, I love this two. Massive amount of blue >_<

2. HaseoAtoli – .hack// G.U. <= Trilogy is good only for HaseoAtoli’s love

3. ZukoMai – Avatar <= love them, emooooooooooooooooooooooooo

4. HirumaMamori – Eyeshield21 <= they’re just fit in my eyes

5. KlavierEma – Gyakuten Saiban <= Glimmerous fop and his Fraulein 😀

5 Titles that Popular Around You but You’re not Interested…

1. Code Geass ~ Lelouch of Rebellion ~ <= don’t know, can’t find anything interesting.

2. KOREAN MANHWA <= not a title, but girls in my class love them. The only Korean Manhwa interest me is ‘Kill Me Kiss Me’, why? The author love D18 😀

3. Tsubasa Chronicle <= not interested. Don’t know what good from this?

4. Suzumiya Haruhi no Yuutsu <= not interested, namely lack of high quality bishiezzz….

5. Lucky Star <= no matter how funny it is, all I know that it’s failed on interest me

5 Titles that You’re Curious about and You Want to Learn More…

1. Gintama <= wanna know, wanna know, wanna know…

2. D. Gray Man <= I’m curious >_<

3. Togainu no Chi <= dead curious about this one

4. Nabari no Ou <= I haven’t learn many things about this one, want to know more….

5. Ookiku Furikabutte <= want to read more!!!

5 Pairings that You Just Ship Recently…

1. GurenMasahiro – Shounen Onmyouji <= Shota corrupt my mind

2. Tsuchiurasukimori – La Corda D’Oro <= hahah, I’m so dead crazy

3. ApolloVera – Gyakuten Saiban <= HET. Not really an OTP, they’re just cute >_<

4. AkihikoKen – Persona 3 <= no matter how many ShinjiAki fans out there, shota win over me

5. RikugouKazane – Shounen Onmyouji <= hahahah, het.

5 Titles that You Never Expected Becoming One of Your Obsession…

1. Kyou Kara Ma Ou! – no kidding. I don’t really like it at first.

2. Shounen Onmyouji – I’m not really interested but the opening song is unresistable,GurenMasacoughcough…

3. Keroro Gunsou – It’s unexpectedly funny for me >_< need more 623!!!

4. Othello – I tought it’s just some shoujo manga but I like it >_<

5. Shugo Chara – because Ikuto is too adoreable to resist

5 Titles that You Know You’ll like Even if You Never Touch it Before… [but You have know]

1. Fullmetal Alchemist <= Roy, long story….

2. Gundam Seed

3. Ookiku Furikabutte

4. Nabari no Ou

5. Katekyo Hitman Reborn

5 Titles That You’re Once Obsessed with But Not Anymore Now… [but you still like it

1. Naruto <= the waiting it’s too long…

2. Gundam Seed <= long story of a long time

3. Fullmetal Alchemist <= still love you Roy-sama

4. Law of Ueki <= Ueki+ failed to catch my attention

5. Rave <= it’s been a years since I last touch them…

5 Genre that You Definitely Like…

1. Angst

2. Adventure

3. Shounen-Ai/Yaoicoughcough

4. Mystery [not horror]

5. Magic

5 Person [Real Person] that You Want to Meet…

1. Haruka Shimotsuki <= I’ll ask her to sing for me >_< and tell her how much I love her

2. Minekura Kazuya <= I heard she’s on a bad condition, I hope she get well

3. Amano Akira <= I’ll scream on her ears;“JUST PAIR 8059 ALREADY!!GET D BACK FOR 18!!”

4. Rurutia <= I need more and more of her >_< !!

5. ELEX MEDIA Director <= ask them to lisence KHR,Oofuri,Wild Adapter,Bus Gamer,& Saiyuki

5 Characters that You Want to Have(?) In Your Room…

1. Dino Cavallone – KHR <= please be my hug pillow

2. AgitoAkito – Air Gear

3. Klavier Gavin – Gyakuten Saiban

4. Aurica Netsmile – Ar Tonelico <= personal MP3 player 😀 *run*

5. Ema Skye – Gyakuten Saiban <= we’ll fight over snackoos & Gavin *snackooed by Ema*

5 Characters that Left The Deepest Imperssion on You…

1. Kai Hiwatari – Beyblade

2. Kaiba Seto – Yugi Oh! <= I got my ‘no pain no gain’ persona from him :p

3. Enzan Ijuuin – Rockaman EXE <= give me your brain, please…. Poor little Enzan

4. Roxas – Kingdom Hearts <= exist, but not exit

5. Gray Michelle Vincent – Battle B-Daman <= ‘I’m not scared of dying, I’m not’

Gape all you want… jawdrop all you want… childish? Very.

5 Fandom That Will Remain Forever In Your Heart…

1. Beyblade

2. Yugi Oh!

3. Rockman EXE

4. Digimon

5. Pokemon

Because these 5 titles left very deep impression on me, despite it’s childish themescoughcough

5 Things You want to be In The Future…

1. RPG Game Designer

2. Translator [in ATLUS/NISA so I can play game from Japancoughcough]

3. Mangaka/Doujinka

4. Prosecutor

5. Mangaka/Doujinka

Ohohohohohhohohho, they’re all about me and my fandom, although there’s still tons of them to be revealed =)
